01:08:36,166 --> 01:08:37,790
Good night.

994
01:08:46,416 --> 01:08:48,540
At the Saviour's command

995
01:08:48,750 --> 01:08:52,249
and formed by divine teaching,
we dare to say:

996
01:08:53,666 --> 01:08:56,999
Our Father who art in heaven,

997
01:08:57,208 --> 01:08:59,999
hallowed be thy name,

998
01:09:00,208 --> 01:09:03,999
thy kingdom come,
thy will be done

999
01:09:04,875 --> 01:09:06,999
on earth, as it is in heaven.

1000
01:09:07,208 --> 01:09:09,207
Looking for me in church now ?

1001
01:09:11,208 --> 01:09:12,874
What's wrong, Tommaso ?

1002
01:09:13,083 --> 01:09:15,082
Nothing, what could be wrong ?

1003
01:09:21,333 --> 01:09:23,457
Do you never feel lonely ?

1004
01:09:23,666 --> 01:09:26,415
No, never, because
I am never on my own.

1005
01:09:26,625 --> 01:09:29,165
And neither are you, because of...

1006
01:09:29,375 --> 01:09:31,457
Not your imaginary friend again !

1007
01:09:36,375 --> 01:09:37,957
Come with me.

1008
01:10:16,666 --> 01:10:19,082
When I'm feeling down,
I come here.

1009
01:10:20,708 --> 01:10:23,290
I discovered this place
one morning, many years ago,

1010
01:10:23,500 --> 01:10:25,707
after I was released from jail.

1011
01:10:26,833 --> 01:10:28,499
Yes, I've been in jail.

1012
01:10:28,708 --> 01:10:32,082
And not just once !
There's lots you don't know about me !

1013
01:10:32,458 --> 01:10:35,082
I might tell you one day.

1014
01:10:35,791 --> 01:10:37,415
We're friends now.

1015
01:10:40,083 --> 01:10:43,582
I didn't know what to do,
so I sat here.

1016
01:10:45,291 --> 01:10:47,540
- And what did you think about ?
- Nothing...

1017
01:10:47,750 --> 01:10:49,415
Nothing at all.

1018
01:10:49,625 --> 01:10:51,540
I was on my own here.

1019
01:10:52,458 --> 01:10:55,832
No desires, no expectations,
no fears.

1020
01:10:57,000 --> 01:10:58,665
Just this.

1021
01:10:59,833 --> 01:11:02,957
Then suddenly,
in a fraction of a second

1022
01:11:04,208 --> 01:11:06,082
it all became clear.

1023
01:11:07,916 --> 01:11:11,165
Three days later I entered
the seminary, and here I am.

1024
01:11:12,875 --> 01:11:16,832
Between you and me, do you
really believe there is a God ?

1025
01:11:17,791 --> 01:11:21,082
- Who do you think God is ?
- I don't know, you're the expert.

1026
01:11:22,750 --> 01:11:25,790
You know those hot summer mornings
when it's really stuffy,

1027
01:11:26,000 --> 01:11:28,582
you open a window
and cool air caresses your face ?

1028
01:11:28,791 --> 01:11:30,582
- That's a breeze.
- No, it's God.

1029
01:11:31,333 --> 01:11:33,832
And when the clouds
take on those strange shapes,

1030
01:11:34,041 --> 01:11:36,415
a horse, a face, a carrot...

1031
01:11:36,625 --> 01:11:38,082
and you keep staring at them...

1032
01:11:38,291 --> 01:11:41,582
- That too is God.
- Who's in church then ?

1033
01:11:42,375 --> 01:11:45,624
Do you think God is happy
to be cooped up in one place ?

1034
01:11:45,833 --> 01:11:48,040
It's not enough, is it ?

1035
01:11:50,000 --> 01:11:51,624
See that pear ?

1036
01:11:53,041 --> 01:11:55,707
Inevitably,
that pear will fall one day.

1037
01:11:57,500 --> 01:11:59,707
Bet you think it's due to gravity.

1038
01:11:59,916 --> 01:12:01,374
No, it's God !

1039
01:12:01,583 --> 01:12:03,749
You're starting to get the idea.

1040
01:12:16,958 --> 01:12:19,082
- Darling, what's wrong ?
- I don't know.

1041
01:12:19,291 --> 01:12:22,957
- I'm always tired.
- You're okay, don't worry.

1042
01:12:23,166 --> 01:12:26,040
- Let me feel your pulse.
- What are you doing ?

1043
01:12:30,750 --> 01:12:34,082
Slight tachycardia.
Let me look at your eye.

1044
01:12:34,291 --> 01:12:36,124
Keep still !

1045
01:12:39,541 --> 01:12:41,707
Nothing serious, don't worry.

1046
01:12:42,416 --> 01:12:44,665
But go to the pharmacy...

1047
01:12:45,708 --> 01:12:47,749
and ask for these tablets.

1048
01:12:48,625 --> 01:12:52,915
Take three a day after meals
for a week.

1049
01:12:55,041 --> 01:12:57,540
And just to be on the safe side,

1050
01:12:57,750 --> 01:13:00,374
have a full check-up done,
okay ?

1051
01:13:00,916 --> 01:13:01,999
Here.

1052
01:13:02,958 --> 01:13:05,999
- Do you want some more pizza ?
- If you insist.

1053
01:13:06,208 --> 01:13:09,040
- Boy !
- Here I am !

1054
01:13:09,250 --> 01:13:11,874
- Two more cheese slices.
- Coming up.

1055
01:13:12,083 --> 01:13:14,374
Said, two cheese slices.
Come on !

1056
01:13:14,583 --> 01:13:17,374
The service is rubbish,
but the pizza's good.

1057
01:14:05,083 --> 01:14:07,999
<<Back to the news in half an hour.>>

1058
01:14:08,208 --> 01:14:11,624
<<I'll leave you with the lyrics>>
<<and music of Gigi D'Alessio !>>

1059
01:15:20,916 --> 01:15:22,790
I was about to call you.

1060
01:15:24,000 --> 01:15:25,624
Have a seat.

1061
01:15:33,125 --> 01:15:35,290
- A drop of wine ?
- No.

1062
01:15:35,500 --> 01:15:36,749
Just a sip.

1063
01:15:48,250 --> 01:15:49,665
Try it.

1064
01:15:49,875 --> 01:15:52,665
I made it,
it was one of your favourites.

1065
01:16:00,750 --> 01:16:02,332
How is it ?

1066
01:16:04,875 --> 01:16:05,957
So so...

1067
01:16:12,708 --> 01:16:14,874
What's with all this ?

1068
01:16:15,083 --> 01:16:17,832
I wanted us to have an evening
all to ourselves.

1069
01:16:21,041 --> 01:16:22,957
You're so beautiful, Carla.

1070
01:16:23,708 --> 01:16:26,374
Tommaso, stop it,
you're scaring me.

1071
01:16:26,583 --> 01:16:28,207
It's the truth.

1072
01:16:28,416 --> 01:16:30,499
Are you courting me ?

1073
01:16:30,708 --> 01:16:32,290
Perhaps.

1074
01:16:33,458 --> 01:16:36,207
You've started taking
the antidepressants again.

1075
01:16:36,416 --> 01:16:37,624
No.

1076
01:16:37,833 --> 01:16:40,249
It's just an excuse really.

1077
01:16:40,458 --> 01:16:42,790
I'm more interested in after dinner.

1078
01:16:45,041 --> 01:16:46,749
I've finished then.

1079
01:16:46,958 --> 01:16:48,582
Don't you want the main dish ?

1080
01:16:48,791 --> 01:16:50,874
Pot roast cooked in Barolo wine.

1081
01:16:51,375 --> 01:16:53,124
Did you make it ?

1082
01:16:53,333 --> 01:16:55,290
I'd better not then.

1083
01:16:58,791 --> 01:17:00,999
- I'll see you tomorrow.
- No.

1084
01:17:01,208 --> 01:17:03,790
- What do you mean ?
- The month is up, you're free.

1085
01:17:04,000 --> 01:17:07,249
We have to remove the stains
from the floors, move the pews...

1086
01:17:07,458 --> 01:17:09,499
I'll take care of that,
you go home !

1087
01:17:10,416 --> 01:17:13,332
- I won't see you again ?
- You can come to Mass on Sunday.

1088
01:17:13,541 --> 01:17:15,832
Then I won't see you again !

1089
01:17:19,416 --> 01:17:20,874
Watch out !

1090
01:17:22,000 --> 01:17:25,124
Listen, let's grab a bite at Said's.

1091
01:17:25,333 --> 01:17:28,749
- I have to work tonight.
- I can't, I have a meeting.

1092
01:17:28,958 --> 01:17:32,374
But if you've nothing to do,
go and talk to Andrea.

1093
01:17:32,583 --> 01:17:34,582
- About what ?
- You know what.

1094
01:17:34,791 --> 01:17:38,582
If you're convinced it's not for him,
you have to tell him.

1095
01:17:40,041 --> 01:17:43,082
I don't know
what to tell him anymore.

1096
01:17:43,291 --> 01:17:46,082
Tell him whatever you want,
just talk to him.

1097
01:17:46,291 --> 01:17:48,249
The time has come, right ?

1098
01:17:48,958 --> 01:17:51,124
Look at this bougainvillea !

1099
01:18:03,500 --> 01:18:04,999
Andrea ?

1100
01:18:06,666 --> 01:18:08,290
Oh, I'm sorry !

1101
01:18:08,916 --> 01:18:10,457
Dad !

1102
01:18:12,291 --> 01:18:13,957
- Dad...
- It's okay.

1103
01:18:14,166 --> 01:18:16,249
- No, let me explain.
- You don't need to.

1104
01:18:16,458 --> 01:18:20,457
Yes, I do.
So much has happened recently.

1105
01:18:20,666 --> 01:18:23,207
During the weeks
at the spiritual retreat...

1106
01:18:24,125 --> 01:18:26,207
I started to have some doubts

1107
01:18:26,416 --> 01:18:29,540
and I thought perhaps
I wasn't cut out for priesthood.

1108
01:18:29,750 --> 01:18:32,290
I know I should have
told you before, but

1109
01:18:32,500 --> 01:18:35,040
I was embarrassed
because I'd changed my mind.

1110
01:18:35,916 --> 01:18:38,374
There's nothing wrong
with changing your mind.

1111
01:18:38,583 --> 01:18:40,665
- I do it a lot myself.
- Is that so ?

1112
01:18:40,875 --> 01:18:43,832
I thought you were the man
of absolute certainties.

1113
01:18:44,916 --> 01:18:47,582
I thought that too.
But no...

1114
01:18:55,083 --> 01:18:57,749
- So no priest for a son ?
- No !

1115
01:18:57,958 --> 01:19:00,874
- Who's going to tell Fr. Pietro ?
- He already knows.

1116
01:19:02,000 --> 01:19:05,415
- What ?
- I told him when he came here.

1117
01:19:06,708 --> 01:19:10,415
So he's known all this time ?

1118
01:19:10,625 --> 01:19:13,665
He convinced me to change paths
because I was too unsure.

1119
01:19:14,250 --> 01:19:16,624
And then I met Alessia
at his meetings,

1120
01:19:16,833 --> 01:19:18,499
the girl you...

1121
01:19:19,041 --> 01:19:22,249
Okay, I have to go. We're going
to Fr. Pietro's meeting later.

1122
01:19:22,458 --> 01:19:24,582
- Bye, Dad.
- Go on.

1123
01:19:26,166 --> 01:19:27,790
The bastard !

1124
01:20:11,333 --> 01:20:13,207
- Hello, darling.
- Hello.

1125
01:20:15,291 --> 01:20:17,707
How long will it be ?
I'm due at the hospital.

1126
01:20:17,916 --> 01:20:20,207
- Five minutes.
- Good.

1127
01:20:20,416 --> 01:20:22,332
I'll go and get changed.

1128
01:20:44,958 --> 01:20:47,124
- Excuse me, professor.
- Yes.

1129
01:20:59,291 --> 01:21:01,290
I got the CT scan results.

1130
01:21:02,375 --> 01:21:04,874
- Well ?
- He has a frontal-parietal hematoma,

1131
01:21:05,083 --> 01:21:06,915
with considerable shift.

1132
01:21:07,125 --> 01:21:09,249
I have to operate immediately.

1133
01:21:11,500 --> 01:21:13,707
De Luca, I'll be honest with you...

1134
01:21:14,750 --> 01:21:16,832
it'd take a miracle.

1135
01:21:18,333 --> 01:21:20,582
Do you want to observe ?

1136
01:21:40,625 --> 01:21:43,957
Sandro, I have to go.
Will you look after the ward ?

1137
01:21:44,166 --> 01:21:45,665
Of course.

1138
01:22:13,875 --> 01:22:16,957
- Well, Dad ?
- The neurosurgeon's a friend of mine.

1139
01:22:17,166 --> 01:22:19,415
He's very good,
he'll do all he can.

1140
01:22:19,625 --> 01:22:21,249
But how is he ?

1141
01:22:21,458 --> 01:22:22,499
Not well.

1142
01:22:22,708 --> 01:22:24,582
He's not well.

1143
01:22:25,500 --> 01:22:27,749
Call me when you get news.

1144
01:22:27,958 --> 01:22:30,915
- Where are you going ?
- I have to do something.
